import React from "react"; import parse from "html-react-parser"; const WhatWeOfferTen = ({ data, tagline, title, backfont }) => (

{tagline}

{title && parse(title)}

{data.slice(0, 2).map((service) => (

{service.title}

{service.text}

))}
{data.slice(2, 4).map((service) => (

{service.title}

{service.text}

))}
); export default WhatWeOfferTen;
